TEXT.TITLE: FIRST FEDERAL BROOKSVILLE<FFBV> ADJOURNS MEETING
TEXT.BODY: First Federal Savings and Loan Association of Brooksville said it has adjourned its annual meeting until May 11 due to the unexpected death of director J.R. Underwood, creating the need for a substitute nominee for the board. Reuter
